Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
