Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.69,0:13:08.19,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,500)}「难道是试胆大会！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.45,0:13:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.14,0:13:15.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到小枫的邮件说是大家来放烟花的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她自己却不在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.62,0:13:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  琴音没和你在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.70,0:13:25.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,她早我两个小时出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.59,0:13:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像带了很多东西的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来那个包裹里好像有长发的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.45,0:13:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,长发是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  这是小枫的留言？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.73,0:13:42.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无视我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了  是不是发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:47.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:53.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就分成两组去找琴音和小枫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来  抽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.20,0:13:58.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是试胆大会！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.28,0:14:02.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大会啊  好久没玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊  好可怕啊春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:07.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在一起就不会有事的  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或许就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:13.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.65,0:14:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.42,0:14:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  我也是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.27,0:14:23.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  春香那是橙色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.25,0:14:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  怎么看都是黄色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.38,0:14:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.42,0:14:32.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  我不能和小优在一起吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要相同颜色的组一队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺带  我是黄色
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.46,0:14:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小雫  我们一组了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:46.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这反应是什么情况啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊  我是队友你不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚感觉完全不会害怕的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,事故感不足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种样子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好可怕～～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.70,0:15:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  没有感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是优还真是对不住了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小优  我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.21,0:15:12.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:13.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,走好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.17,0:15:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优她离我而去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小雫  我们一起吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:33.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小柚～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.25,0:15:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,于是进行了交换
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.39,0:15:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那春香你们10分钟后跟来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.89,0:15:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.65,0:15:45.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  没问题吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在还来得及回头哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.97,0:15:49.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你又在耍我！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香你也只有现在能说说风凉话了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真要有什么情况我可不救你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.30,0:15:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉  我随口说说的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:00.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,十分钟后
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:03.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.49,0:16:06.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样也好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,尾随而来的美月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优这孩子  居然这么晚还到这种地方来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.50,0:16:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.22,0:16:21.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  果然和春香同学在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.90,0:16:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还好平时在头饰上涂了萤光涂料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过话说回来这地方还真让人不怎么舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能害怕  想点什么开心的事再尾随吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:47.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开心的事…  开心的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.49,0:16:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月会长  张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:53.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能是春香同学啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么会想起春香同学啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…春香  刚刚有没有看到什么东西在闪光？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.01,0:17:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是我的错觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.17,0:17:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出现啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下啊  小优
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.14,0:17:19.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别把我扔下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:24.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  一下子就传出了悲鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是…看到了什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.19,0:17:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟过来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.08,0:17:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优  你在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.52,0:17:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.27,0:17:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好像有什么东西跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办  要是跟到这里来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.18,0:17:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.76,0:17:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优在害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.91,0:17:57.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吻…吻我一下或许就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定真会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.80,0:18:02.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的  小优…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.98,0:18:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  吻我一下或许就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被看穿了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:10.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  居然这么害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.99,0:18:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要说怪物也是小枫或者琴音的其中一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.27,0:18:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  春香…快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,心中有什么东西觉醒了的春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.49,0:18:30.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.16,0:18:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到我平静下来以前  请一直吻着我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.63,0:18:54.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,停不下来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.97,0:18:59.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次我一定要让你平静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:11.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优？优  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:18.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在叫我的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,优！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.54,0:19:23.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了  优
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.87,0:19:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美月会长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.70,0:19:27.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐  你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.54,0:19:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是跟在你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:35.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么会抱在一起啊  给我分开！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.16,0:19:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之姐姐  赶紧从这里出去比较好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.21,0:19:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚才就在被人喊着名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.50,0:19:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.44,0:19:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别开玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.92,0:19:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别吓唬你姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.23,0:19:51.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.97,0:19:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是春香同学一边喊着优的名字一边在接吻吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.36,0:19:59.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.79,0:20:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才没有喊名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:05.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐你整天就这么想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.54,0:20:10.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就别吵了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别走散了  一起行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:13.50,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,注：投怀送抱之后的左拥右抱之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.07,0:20:17.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不必了  我就一个人回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,跟春香同学靠那么近  我的心脏受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.31,0:20:25.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,害怕就害怕了  不用不好意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:28.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人在一起就不会害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是这么回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就当作是这样好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:42.52,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,再注：顺理成章之姐妹丼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.32,0:20:47.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.56,0:20:57.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？大家都在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  优  好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.41,0:21:03.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.55,0:21:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没说是试胆大会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.40,0:21:09.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.21,0:21:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了来放烟花的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.88,0:21:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.50,0:21:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还搞抽签什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  似乎多了个不该存在的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.20,0:21:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,本来是想搞试胆大会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只准备了烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.32,0:21:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,试胆大会明年再弄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.36,0:21:33.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你好不容易做了些签
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:35.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得不抽太浪费了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.22,0:21:45.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那跟在我后面叫我名字的是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:47.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么  别说了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.07,0:21:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就只做了烟花的准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.17,0:21:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.31,0:21:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小优  冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.34,0:22:06.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,春香同学真是个体贴的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.88,title1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,710)\fs45}「难道是试胆大会！？」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:09.88,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(400,710)\fs45}「难道是试胆大会！？」
