Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜欢炒面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.31,0:23:48.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然炒面我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.29,0:23:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.32,0:23:53.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是在海边小店吃的炒面最棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我更喜欢杯面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.20,0:23:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦！
